# Build: $ doxygen
# Check: $ open build/docs/index.html
# Note:
# - Every documentation page (.dox) MUST be wrapped with /** ... */
# - Every public header file (.h) MUST begin with a /** \file ... */
# - Every public definition MUST have a non-empty /** ... */

# Seriously though, why should generating usable C documentation be so cumbersome?
# I only managed to get Doxygen docs look okay-ish through heavy customization

